# Codebase Awareness

## Frontend Module Map

```
src/app/
  (public)/           → public user-facing routes
    page.tsx           → Home
    about/             → About
    services/          → Services
    projects/          → Projects
    government/        → Government
    government-review/ → Government Review
    submit/            → Submit a Project
    privacy/           → Privacy Policy (RSC — reads legal_privacy setting)
    terms/             → Terms of Service (RSC — reads legal_terms setting)
  (admin)/
    layout.tsx         → requireAdmin() guard
    admin/page.tsx     → DashboardPage
    admin/leads/       admin/projects/  admin/documents/
    admin/content/     admin/audit/     admin/settings/
    admin/faq/         → FaqManager
    admin/announcement/→ AnnouncementManager
    admin/section-visibility/ → SectionVisibilityManager
    admin/maintenance/ → MaintenanceManager
    admin/legal/       → LegalPagesEditor
  maintenance/         → standalone maintenance page (no layout)
  api/auth/            → JWT route handlers (login, logout, refresh)

src/modules/admin/
  dashboard/   → DashboardPage, stats.service.ts, useDashboardStats, useProjectStats
  leads/       → LeadsTable, leads.service.ts, useLeads, useUpdateLead
  projects/    → ProjectsTable, projects.service.ts, useAdminProjects, useCreateProject, useUpdateProject, useDeleteProject
  documents/   → DocumentsTable, documents.service.ts, useDocuments, useCreateDocument, useUpdateDocument, useDeleteDocument
  faqs/        → FaqManager, faqs.service.ts, useFaqs, useCreateFaq, useUpdateFaq, useDeleteFaq
  content/     → ContentPage, SiteSettingsManager, BrandingManager, NavigationManager,
                  TeamManager, ServicesManager, TestimonialsManager, ContentStatsManager,
                  MethodologyManager, AboutEditor, ImagesEditor,
                  AnnouncementManager, MaintenanceManager, LegalPagesEditor, SectionVisibilityManager
                  content.service.ts (stats/methodology/testimonials/services)
                  site-settings.service.ts (useGetSiteSettings, useUpdateSiteSettings)
  audit/       → AuditLogViewer, audit.service.ts, useAuditLogs, useClearAuditLogs
  settings/    → SettingsPanel
  auth/        → auth.service.ts, auth.validator.ts
  shared/      → AdminSidebar, AdminHeader, StatusBadge, TableToolbar
                  useDebouncedSearch, useTableFilters
  modals/      → InterestsModal, PreviewModal

src/modules/public/
  home/        → home.service.ts
  projects/    → projects.service.ts, interest.service.ts
  legal/       → LegalPageView (shared RSC renderer for privacy + terms)
  modals/      → ExpressInterestModal
  shared/      → shared public UI

src/components/common/
  Navbar.tsx          → dynamic nav (no sticky — FR-HEADER-001)
  Footer.tsx
  AnnouncementBar.tsx → server component (reads announcement_bar setting)

src/lib/
  actions/admin.ts   → all admin Server Actions + requireAdmin()
  actions/public.ts  → submitLead, expressInterest
  api-helpers/       → axios-instance.ts (apiAxios), client.ts (apiClient), parse-error.ts
  url-helpers/       → routes.ts (ROUTES.*), api-endpoints.ts (API.*)
  constants/         → branding.ts (BRAND.*), site.ts, env.ts
  types/domain.ts    → Lead, Project, Document, CatalogService, Testimonial,
                        ContentStat, MethodologyStep, SiteSetting, AuditLog,
                        DashboardStats, ProjectStats, Faq
  validators/        → lead.ts, project.ts, document.ts, service.ts, interest.ts, content.ts
  auth.ts            → verifySession(), requireAdmin()
  store/             → modal.store.ts, admin-filters.store.ts
  site-settings.ts   → ⚠️ NOT YET CREATED — getSectionVisibility() server helper
```

## Backend Module Map

```
src/modules/
  auth/         → login, verify, logout, refresh, change-password,
                  setup-status, setup, reset-password + requireAuth middleware
  leads/        → public POST /leads · protected GET/PATCH /leads/:id
  projects/     → public GET · protected POST/PATCH/DELETE + interests
  documents/    → all protected (GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE)
  services/     → public GET · protected POST/PATCH/DELETE
  faqs/         → public GET /content/faqs · protected POST/PATCH/DELETE
  content/      → public GET stats/methodology/settings/faqs · protected mutations
                  SETTING_DEFAULTS: hero, footer, branding, seo_*, navigation, about,
                  services_page, government_page, submit_page, announcement_bar,
                  maintenance_mode, legal_privacy, legal_terms, section_visibility
  testimonials/ → public GET · protected POST/PATCH/DELETE
  stats/        → protected /stats + /stats/projects
  audit/        → protected GET/DELETE /audit
  notifications/→ protected /notifications/status + /notifications/test

src/db/schema/  → leads, projects, project_interests, documents, services,
                  content_stats, methodology_steps, site_settings, testimonials,
                  audit_logs, users, sessions, faqs
src/shared/
  middleware/require-auth.ts   → JWT validation
  url-helpers/route-paths.ts   → ROUTE_PATHS.*
  api-helpers/                 → parseIdParam, sendJson
  lib/email.ts                 → sendInquiryNotification (Resend)
```
